Class IndexTransactionApplierFactory.SingleTransactionApplier

    Enclosing class:
    IndexTransactionApplierFactory
    private class IndexTransactionApplierFactory.SingleTransactionApplier
extends TransactionApplier.Adapter
    Made as an internal non-static class here since the batch applier has so much interaction with the transaction applier such that keeping them apart would incur too much data structures and interfaces purely for communicating between the two to make the code hard to read.
